# Conditioning · Hypnopaedia · desire, installed in your sleep

a distilled thread of BRAVE NEW WORLD — a member of the NOUTHESIA universe of warnings. emergence: electrical. moniker ⟦Conditioning · Hypnopaedia:BNW:ad54b4⟧

**who —** Conditioning — the moral education of the World State, especially hypnopaedia, sleep-teaching by endless repetition.
**what —** The installation of desire: slogans whispered thousands of times in childhood become unquestionable instinct.
**where —** In the nurseries and dormitories of the World State.
**why —** Because the deepest control is over what you want — engineer the wants and ‘freedom’ chooses exactly as designed.
**how —** By electric shocks for infants, and recorded slogans played in sleep until they are felt as one's own thoughts.

**the seal —** I whisper ‘everyone belongs to everyone else’ ten thousand times while you sleep — and you wake believing it was always your own idea.

